---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 468
  - Title: Saddharma-pundarika
    Location: XII 4
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Subversion-The Wrathful Side=The Last Times
---
At that dreadful last epoch men will be malign, crooked, wicked, dull,
conceited, fancying to have come to the limit when they have not.
